 post in mozilla.dev.security.policy newsgroup</ref><ref>[http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2017-11-20/doc-ifynwxum6288539.shtml 国内证书颁发机构StartCom宣布将停止数字证书业务] {{Wayback|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2017-11-20/doc-ifynwxum6288539.shtml |date=20171120035831 }}，新浪科技</ref>。

== StartSSL ==
StartCom提供免费的Class 1 [[X.509|X.509]] SSL证书“StartSSL Free”，可用于网站服务器（[[傳輸層安全協議|SSL/TLS]]）和{{tsl|en|E-mail encryption|电子邮件加密}}（[[S/MIME|S/MIME]]）。StartCom还提供Class 2和3的证书，以及[[扩展验证证书|扩展验证证书]]，需要复杂的验证（收费）才能得到。

2011年6月，该公司遭受网络攻击，被迫暂停数字证书发放及相关服务数周<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2011/06/21/startssl_security_breach/|title=Web authentication authority suffers security breach|accessdate=2012-01-14|date=2011-06-26|publisher=[[The_Register|The Register]]|language=en|archive-date=2012-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104225508/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2011/06/21/startssl_security_breach/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。攻击者无法借此机会颁发证书（在被攻击的6家机构中，只有StartCom成功阻止攻击者的颁发尝试）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.informationweek.com/security/attacks/how-startcom-foiled-comodohacker-4-lesso/231601037 |title=How StartCom Foiled Comodohacker: 4 Lessons |accessdate=2012-12-20 |date=2011-09-08 |publisher={{tsl|en|InformationWeek}} |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130103030451/http://www.informationweek.com/security/attacks/how-startcom-foiled-comodohacker-4-lesso/231601037 |archivedate=2013-01-03 }}</ref>。

=== 可信度 ===
StartSSL证书在以下环境中默认启用：[[Firefox|Mozilla Firefox]] 2.x或更高版本，Apple Mac OS X [[Mac_OS_X_Leopard|10.5 (Leopard)]]或更高版本，2009年9月24日后所有[[微软|微软]]操作系统<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.startcom.org/?app=14&rel=33|title=Microsoft Adds Support for StartCom Certificates|accessdate=2011-01-14|date=2009-09-24|format=新闻稿|publisher=StartCom.org|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717142400/http://www.startcom.org/?app=14&rel=33|archivedate=2011-07-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sophos.com/blogs/chetw/g/2009/09/27/microsoft-updates-root-certs-startcom/|title=Microsoft updates trusted root certs to include StartCom|date=2009-09-27|publisher=Sophos.com Naked Security blog|language=en}}</ref>，以及2010年7月27日后的[[Opera電腦瀏覽器|Opera]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://my.opera.com/rootstore/blog/2010/07/28/new-roots-new-ev-and-a-new-public-suffix-file|title=New Roots, new EV, and a new Public Suffix file|publisher=Opera.com Rootstore blog|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2010-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100801232344/http://my.opera.com/rootstore/blog/2010/07/28/new-roots-new-ev-and-a-new-public-suffix-file|dead-url=no}}</ref>。因为[[Google_Chrome|Google Chrome]]，[[Safari|Apple Safari]]和[[Internet_Explorer|Internet Explorer]]使用操作系统的证书库，所有主流浏览器都支持StartSSL证书。

2016年9月30日，在对沃通的调查期间，苹果宣布旗下软件不会接受2016年9月19日后由沃通CA签发的证书，并会随调查进展对WoSign/StartCom的信任锚采取进一步行动。

2016年10月24日，Mozilla在其安全博客上宣布，由于在对证书颁发机构沃通数个问题的调查中发现它收购了StartCom，而交易双方并未披露此事<ref name="mozillawiki">{{Cite web|url=https://wiki.mozilla.org/CA:WoSign_Issues|title=CA:WoSign Issues - MozillaWiki|accessdate=2016-10-25|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028085410/https://wiki.mozilla.org/CA:WoSign_Issues|dead-url=no}}</ref>，Mozilla将从Firefox 51开始，停止信任2016年10月21日后签发的证书<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blog.mozilla.org/security/2016/10/24/distrusting-new-wosign-and-startcom-certificates/|title=Distrusting New WoSign and StartCom Certificates|accessdate=2016-10-25|date=2016-10-24|language=en|archive-date=2016-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025175628/https://blog.mozilla.org/security/2016/10/24/distrusting-new-wosign-and-startcom-certificates/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年9月1日，Google也宣布会从Chrome 56开始停止信任上述证书<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://security.googleblog.com/2016/10/distrusting-wosign-and-startcom.html|title=Distrusting WoSign and StartCom Certificates|newspaper=Google Online Security Blog|accessdate=2016-11-02|language=en|archive-date=2016-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101230053/https://security.googleblog.com/2016/10/distrusting-wosign-and-startcom.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年9月30日，苹果产品将阻止由沃通和StartCom根CA签发，且生效日期在2016年12月1日00:00:00 GMT/UTC或其后的证书<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204132|title=Lists of available trusted root certificates in iOS|newspaper=Apple Support Web Site|accessdate=2016-12-01|language=en|archive-date=2016-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161129150700/https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT204132|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年7月8日，Google 宣布将完全取消对沃通和 StartCom 所有证书的信任，包括过去签发的证书。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=53016|title=Solidot {{!}} Google 将完全取消沃通和 StartCom 的信任|accessdate=2017-07-11|work=www.solidot.org|archive-date=2017-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712040225/http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=53016|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/forum/#!topic/net-dev/FKXe-76GO8Y|title=Google 网上论坛|accessdate=2017-07-11|work=groups.google.com|archive-date=2013-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523081122/http://groups.google.com/a/chromium.org/group/chromium-os-dev/browse_thread/thread/337cca9a0da59ad6/9354a38894da5df5#!topic/net-dev/FKXe-76GO8Y|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2017年7月11日，Firefox也准备完全取消对沃通, Startcom 和 CNNIC 的信任。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=53044|title=Solidot {{!}} 火狐准备完全取消对沃通、Startcom 和 CNNIC 的信任|accessdate=2017-07-11|work=www.solidot.org|archive-date=2017-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170722235618/http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=53044|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== StartSSL无限免费证书的限制 ===
尽管在特定用途下是免费且可无限签发的，这些证书仍有一些限制，需付费升级才能解除：
* 3年的证书有效期
* 证书吊销需付费

=== 对Heartbleed的应对 ===
2014年4月13日，StartCom发布了<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/startssl/status/455264672892342272|title=Twitter / startssl: We released a small FAQ page ...|date=2014-04-13|publisher=StartCom|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318013943/https://twitter.com/startssl/status/455264672892342272|dead-url=no}}</ref>一个FAQ页面<ref name="startcom-heartbleed-faq">{{Cite web|url=https://www.startssl.com/?app=43|title=Heartbleed F.A.Q.|date=2014-04-13|publisher=StartCom|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307120100/http://startssl.com/?app=43|dead-url=no}}</ref>，内容有关OpenSSL中的严重漏洞[[心脏出血漏洞|Heartbleed]]，后者据估计会使互联网上17%的安全网页服务器面临数据失窃的风险。

StartCom的政策对吊销一张证书收费25美元，并且拒绝对受Heartbleed影响的证书免除这笔费用，只有部分付费客户可免费吊销一张证书<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=7557845|title=I use StartCom, and I revoked and re-keyed yesterday. In the revocation reason, ... Hacker News|date=2014-04-09|publisher=Geoff|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203061156/https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=7557845|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/codeawe/status/454504028169584640|title=Twitter / codeawe: @tonylampada @startssl ...|date=2014-04-11|publisher=J. Breitsprecher|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2014-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414232301/https://twitter.com/codeawe/status/454504028169584640|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://forum.startcom.org/viewtopic.php?p=8097#p8097 |title=Re: OpenSSL CVE-2014-0160 (aka "Heartbleed") |date=2014-04-09 |publisher=Jan |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404210016/https://forum.startcom.org/viewtopic.php?p=8097#p8097 |archivedate=2016-04-04 |language=en |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2017-02-25 }}</ref><ref name="startcom-heartbleed-5-hours">{{Cite web |url=https://forum.startcom.org/viewtopic.php?p=8101#p8101 |title=Re: OpenSSL CVE-2014-0160 (aka "Heartbleed") |date=2014-04-10 |publisher=arnowelzel |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404030316/https://forum.startcom.org/viewtopic.php?p=8101#p8101 |archivedate=2016-04-04 |language=en |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2017-02-25 }}</ref>，这使得很多人对StartCom是否是合格的证书颁发机构产生怀疑<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=994033|title=Most StartSSL certs will stay compromised|date=2014-04-09|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203061221/https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=994033|dead-url=no}}</ref>。对于已被证明不可信的证书，StartCom拒绝免费吊销，而是在明知的情况下继续提供信任<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://revokame.tonylampada.com.br/|title=StartSSL, please revoke me!|date=2014-04-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412085458/https://revokame.tonylampada.com.br/|archivedate=2014-04-12|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 批评 ==
2016年8月，StartCom被中国证书机构沃通收购<ref name="percya-purchase">{{Cite web|url=http://www.percya.com/2016/09/wosigns-secret-purchase-of-startcom.html|title=Thoughts and Observations: WoSign's secret purchase of StartCom; WoSign threatened legal actions over the disclosure|accessdate=2016-09-08|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160905173058/http://www.percya.com/2016/09/wosigns-secret-purchase-of-startcom.html|archive-date=2016-09-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.percya.com/2016/09/startcom-operated-solely-in-china.html|title=Thoughts and Observations: StartCom operated solely by WoSign in China - an analysis of the new StartCom website|accessdate=2016-09-08|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160907132911/http://www.percya.com/2016/09/startcom-operated-solely-in-china.html|archive-date=2016-09-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，对此事的最初披露文章因法律原因已被删除<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.letsphish.org/?part=about|title=Can you trust them?|accessdate=2017-02-25|work=www.letsphish.org|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160901113828/https://www.letsphish.org/?part=about|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但相关转发仍然存在。尽管具体关系不明，但在沃通被发现签发约100张<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://groups.google.com/d/topic/mozilla.dev.security.policy/k9PBmyLCi8I/discussion |title=Google 网上论坛 |accessdate=2017-02-25 |work=groups.google.com |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20170225041206/https://groups.google.com/forum/%23!topic/mozilla.dev.security.policy/k9PBmyLCi8I/discussion%5B1-25%5D |archivedate=2017-02-25 |language=en |deadurl=yes }}</ref>不当SSL证书时似乎已在使用StartCom的技术设施，这些不当证书中包括一张签发给github.com的证书<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.schrauger.com/the-story-of-how-wosign-gave-me-an-ssl-certificate-for-github-com|title=The story of how WoSign gave me an SSL certificate for GitHub.com|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-25|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317182537/https://www.schrauger.com/the-story-of-how-wosign-gave-me-an-ssl-certificate-for-github-com|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

